title: Mock Draft Monday with Ryan Wilson, Chip Patterson (Football 2/18)
description:
Will Brinson is joined by Ryan Wilson and Chip Patterson to do another full 2019 NFL Mock Draft, making picks for every single team 1-32 and then to chat about some of the AAF action from the weekend.
